room_title: Escape room "Z51" by Can You Escape? LI in New York
room_description: An extraterrestrial parasite has contaminated the lead scientist in the Underborn Labs, they have set a bomb to self-destruct. Not only will their research lab be destroyed but so will the local area. It is up to you to stabilize the cure, disinfect the scientist and stop the bomb from detonating. You are our last hope! Can you escape the research facility in time?
